     H            Y.
     F** UTLR30   ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : RETRIEVE GENTRAN FILE LOCK USER                *
     F*  WRITTEN    : 10/26/2016                                     *
     F*  WRITTEN BY : JW (SRA)                                       *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR30'
     F*                    PARM           $FILE  10
     F*                    PARM           $WSID  10
     F*                    PARM           $USER  10
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $FILE : 10A FILE
     F*       $WSID : 10A WORKSTATION
     F*   OUT $USER : 10A USER ID
     F*       $RTN  :  1A RETORN CODE (*=ERROR)
     F****************************************************************
     FTXTP132 IF  E                    DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1 132 WTXT
     I                                        4  13 WFILE
     I                                       15  24 WWSID
     I                                       26  35 WUSER
     I                                       37  42 WNO
     I                                       80  83 WSCP
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     I              '0123456789'          C         NUM
      ******************************************************
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      ******************************************************
      * INITIAL SET
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      * LOOP
     C           *IN91     DOWEQ*OFF
     C                     READ TXTP132                  91
      * IF RECORD EXISTS
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELTXT132    WTXT
      * IGNORE HEADER
     C           WSCP      IFEQ '*JOB'
     C                     MOVELWFILE     $FILE
     C                     MOVELWWSID     $WSID
     C                     MOVELWUSER     $USER
     C                     MOVEL'*'       $RTN
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      ******************************************************
      *                  INITIAL ROUTINE
      ******************************************************
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $FILE  10
     C                     PARM           $WSID  10
     C                     PARM           $USER  10
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
